{"data":[{"date":"06:30 18/07","title":"M\u1eb9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft c\u00f3c","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/18/me-tuyen-thu-brazil-tham-du-world-cup-2018-bi-bat-coc.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4318","checkdouble":"191468"},{"date":"06:33 18/07","title":"Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u HLV Conte tr\u00ean MXH","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/18/lien-doan-bong-da-anh-che-gieu-hlv-conte-tren-mxh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qua t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Twitter FA Cup, FA d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111em c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea ra l\u00e0m tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a sau khi t\u00e1n d\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Willian.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man Utd trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft FA Cup m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, Willian \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u00ean c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng khi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh Chelsea \u0103n m\u1eebng ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng che \u0111i HLV Conte b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil ngay sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00f3a b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa l\u1ea1i n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a c\u1ee7a FA. T\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Twitter FA Cup c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh (FA) \u0111\u0103ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh n\u00e0y k\u00e8m theo d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i: \"Gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Willian\".\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh FA ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u HLV Conte tr\u00ean MXH h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh FA ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u HLV Conte tr\u00ean MXH h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/4E57A1E2000005785962431imagea63_1531830060814.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh k\u00e8m d\u00f2ng tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00f3a \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean. \u1ea2nh: Twitter.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu b\u00e3o ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean. B\u1edfi l\u1ebd, HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eeba chia tay Chelsea sau 2 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, song \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ecbp mang v\u1ec1 cho ph\u00f2ng truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CLB n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League v\u00e0 FA Cup.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @itsfaizan th\u1eafc m\u1eafc: \"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 trang ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a FA Cup kh\u00f4ng v\u1eady?\". Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n @demar_inuh t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu: \"Qu\u1ea3n tr\u1ecb vi\u00ean bao nhi\u00eau tu\u1ed5i r\u1ed3i? Th\u1eadt l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ngu xu\u1ea9n. \u0110\u00e0o b\u1edbi l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh vi thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Willian v\u1edbi HLV c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u01b0? L\u00e0m t\u1ed1t l\u1eafm\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chia tay v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italy ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 61 t\u1eeb. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u00fac Conte th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c HLV n\u00e0y \"b\u1eadt b\u00e3i\" kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tin nh\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 k\u00e9o theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi r\u01a1i kh\u1ecfi top 4 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n chung c\u1ee7a CLB trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ef1u HLV Juventus \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Napoli thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ea1i Seria A m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4317","checkdouble":"191469"},{"date":"19:40 17/07","title":"Tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/tin-tuc-moi-nhat-ve-chan-thuong-cua-tien-ve-tuan-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb CLB HAGL, ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn, ng\u00f4i sao HAGL c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 t\u1edbi.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111ang b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c kh\u00e1 nhanh t\u1ea1i H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tin t\u1ee9c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Tu\u1ea5n Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/u23-viet-nam-chot-danh-sach-tuan-anh-bao-tin-vui-tu-han-quoc1531820892.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2 V-League 2018. Theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1eeb b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh b\u1ecb r\u1ea1n s\u1ee5n l\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u ngo\u00e0i kh\u1edbp g\u1ed1i ph\u1ea3i (5x7mm), ph\u00f9 n\u1ec1 d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng ch\u00e9o tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ph\u00f9 n\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee5n ch\u00eam ngo\u00e0i v\u00e0 t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u00e2n c\u01a1 khoeo.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a sang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u0129 Choi Joo Yong l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng Park Ji Sung. Ca ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 qu\u00ea Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB HAGL c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n 2 bu\u1ed5i ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb th\u1ee9 2 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ee9 7, Tu\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u1ebfn b\u1ec7nh vi\u1ec7n ho\u1eb7c ph\u00f2ng gym \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo gi\u00e1o \u00e1n c\u1ee7a b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 Choi Joo Young.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Tu\u1ea5n Anh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10. C\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u1ef9 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0 CLB HAGL \u0111ang ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap &lsquo;Nh\u00f4&rsquo; c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbp l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay. C\u00f2n nh\u1edb n\u0103m 2016, Tu\u1ea5n Anh c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFF Cup n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-168-191435.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-168-191435.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00f3t hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4316","checkdouble":"191459"},{"date":"20:48 17/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018b\u1ecf qu\u00ean\u2019 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>1. H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i &ndash; B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i khi m\u00e0 Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 th\u0103ng hoa v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng hoa m\u1ef9 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG Th\u00e1i Lan, Tristan Do. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng l\u00fac c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u1eeb HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 19 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Song c\u00f3 l\u1ebd do v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i n\u00ean T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\" target=\"_blank\">danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span>&nbsp;\u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ho Tan Tai\" title=\"H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/21/u19-viet-nam-ho-tan-tai-ruc-sang-o-tran-dau-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u1ed3 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ecb 'b\u1ecf qu\u00ean' \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>2. Tr\u1ea7n V\u0103n Ki\u00ean &ndash; H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div>V\u0103n Ki\u00ean ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc nh\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. L\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 19 tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng Moses, Duy M\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 n\u0103m nay m\u1edbi 22 tu\u1ed5i song V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi vai tr\u00f2 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Ch\u00ednh anh c\u0169ng t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n V\u0103n Thanh, V\u0103n S\u01a1n &ndash; nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecf qua V\u0103n Ki\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>3. B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Ki\u00ean v\u00e0 T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean t\u1ea1i<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\"> V-League</span> n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o &lsquo;m\u1eaft xanh&rsquo; HLV Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 16 tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Thanh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n anh t\u1ea1i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y n\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ebd th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/7/30/Nhung-guong-mat-bi-HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-&lsquo;bo-quen&rsquo;-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ebfn D\u1ee5ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh v\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Phan V\u0103n Long<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Phan V\u0103n Long c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp. H\u1ed3i cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, V\u0103n Long t\u1eebng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn anh l\u1ee1 h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB, Phan V\u0103n Long c\u0169ng g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do V\u0103n Long kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y Park.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 b\u1ecb b\u1ecf qu\u00ean \u1edf ASIAD 2018, Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong 3 su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean tu\u1ed5i 23.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc b\u1edfi trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua, trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 v\u00e0 \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chu\u1ed7i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Mr. Park \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y n\u00ean \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1ecdi Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"que ngoc hai\" title=\"que ngoc hai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/9/ly-do-khien-que-ngoc-hai-bi-loai-khoi-dt-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf&nbsp;Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i \u1edf h\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>6. H\u1ed3 Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1eafc Ng\u1ecdc c\u0169ng l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p v\u00e0o chu\u1ed7i 7 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 SLNA. Trong \u0111\u1ee3t h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110TQG g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y g\u1eb7p Jordan, anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung ra s\u00e2n, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 3 su\u1ea5t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean \u00f4ng Park mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>7. \u0110inh Thanh Trung<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thanh Trung c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp. M\u00f9a n\u00e0y QBV Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2017 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thanh Trung vs Campuchia\" title=\"Thanh Trung vs Campuchia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/10/10/Xuan-Truong-va-nhung-ai-phu-hop-deo-bang-doi-truong-DT-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Thanh Trung c\u0169ng b\u1ecb th\u1ea7y Park b\u1ecf qua \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh ra s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ee7 19 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00fa hat-trick v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u. Song \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 anh thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o&nbsp;danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1eadp trung s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-168-191435.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ldbd-chau-a-muon-boc-tham-lai-mon-bong-da-nam-asiad-168-191435.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 AFC \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 s\u00f3t hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n UAE v\u00e0 Palestine.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\"></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4315","checkdouble":"191462"},{"date":"18:29 17/07","title":"PSG: \"Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/17/psg-neymar-da-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Luis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Neymar l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Barca t\u1edbi PSG v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 222 tri\u1ec7u euro.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Luis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/6/Luis-Fernandez-phat-bieu-ve-Neymar-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, song \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n cho r\u1eb1ng \u201cti\u1ec3u Pele\u201d mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Cavani v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi NHM l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Neymar mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/nong-real-madrid-du-chi-hon-400-trieu-usd-de-mua-neymar-180-188194.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real quan t\u00e2m Neymar</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Luis Fernandez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi PSG, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Neymar, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi Neymar mong mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00eda Real Madrid c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar, h\u1ecd kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i. Los Blancos c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Neymar \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mbappe c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Neymar th\u00ec Mbappe c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Real, Barca hay MU l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe\" title=\"Mbappe\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/ferdinand-khuyen-mu-chieu-mo-mbappe-bang-moi-gia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mbappe c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Luis Fernandez c\u1ee7a PSG kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mbappe c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf PSG v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u c\u1ea3. Mbappe c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn c\u00f9ng PSG \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4314","checkdouble":"191453"},{"date":"18:44 17/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/7: PSG ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-177-psg-chot-tuong-lai-neymar-va-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/7.</h2><h2>Liverpool d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ee5 Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Gazzetta dello Sport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool \u0111ang v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean gi\u00e0nh pole \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson t\u1eeb Roma. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 70 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Roma \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd Chelsea nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00ean h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe \u1edf l\u1ea1i PSG\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 177 PSG ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 177 PSG ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/day-3-muc-tieu-hang-dau-duoc-real-nham-thay-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 17/7: PSG ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Luis Hernandez c\u1ee7a PSG m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed. C\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real Madrid, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 sau khi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng Luis Hernandez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3 hai ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay PSG trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<h2>Man City b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c v\u1ee5 Kovacic</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Sky Sports \u0111\u01b0a tin Man City s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi ra s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ee5 Kovacic nh\u01b0 ph\u00eda Real y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Man xanh hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang lao v\u00e0o th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m sau khi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Jorginho \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1. Nh\u01b0ng con s\u1ed1 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Real y\u00eau c\u1ea7u l\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante h\u01a1n Willian</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u00ean gia Graham Hunter c\u1ee7a Sky Sports cho bi\u1ebft Barcelona s\u1ebd g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1edbi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Kante thay v\u00ec Willian. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea b\u00e2y gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ec5 khi HLV Sarri kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng l\u1ea1i The Blues.</div>\r\n<h2>Sao Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ebfn Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Andre Gomes \u0111ang t\u00ednh s\u1ebd gia nh\u1eadp Tottenham h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Camp Nou sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i cho th\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<h2>PSG nh\u1eafm sao Tottenham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Le10 Sport cho bi\u1ebft PSG \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Danny Rose c\u1ee7a Spurs. Nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Ligue 1 \u0111ang nh\u1eafm b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 sau khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i Yuri Berchiche ra \u0111i. Rose tuy kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh PSG.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-177-ronaldo-vo-tinh-bao-hai-man-utd-184-191403.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 17/7: Ronaldo v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh b\u00e1o h\u1ea1i Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-167-sao-tre-mbappe-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-184-191376.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/7: Sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4313","checkdouble":"191458"},{"date":"20:55 17/07","title":"\"Ronaldo s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/ronaldo-se-hoi-han-voi-quyet-dinh-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Christian Panucci d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real.</h2><h2>Panucci c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panucci t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga, Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Champions League v\u00e0 C\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB trong 3 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 x\u01b0a. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Marcelo Lippi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 45 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Serie A. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng CR7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo r\u1eddi  Real, nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Panucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo r\u1eddi  Real, nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Panucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/ronaldo-se-hoi-han-voi-quyet-dinh-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Panucci c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn khi r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi t\u00f4i r\u1eddi Real, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3.</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. N\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng ra th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Juventus. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00f4i k\u00e9o nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Italia. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ADN c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Panucci d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian chuy\u1ec3n giao kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi HLV Zinedine <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/soc-zidane-bat-ngo-tu-chuc-hlv-real-madrid-180-187457.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zidane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZidane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng La Liga \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. V\u00e0 Panucci cho r\u1eb1ng Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Ronaldo c\u0169ng ra \u0111i. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf h\u1ecd v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Champions League\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191416.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-real-180-191412.html\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV tai ti\u1ebfng t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4312","checkdouble":"191461"},{"date":"22:45 17/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/31/hazard-can-phai-chuyen-den-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Craig Burley cho r\u1eb1ng Hazard c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i theo g\u01b0\u01a1ng Ronaldo, t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Premier League v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Burley khuy\u00ean Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real</span> Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Craig Burley c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-can-phai-chuyen-den-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Burley cho r\u1eb1ng Hazard c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cHazard \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 n\u0103m. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3. Nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Chelsea. Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid khi h\u1ecd ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng? V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi Ronaldo r\u1eddi Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac Hazard \u0111i l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Hazard \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea sau khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 6 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 ph\u00eda n\u1eafm quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cSau 6 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Chelsea, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i khai ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, sau k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf. Nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u00e0 b\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jorginho-chia-khoa-thanh-cong-cua-sarri-172-191455.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho: Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191438.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4311","checkdouble":"191463"},{"date":"06:19 18/07","title":"Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/15/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Andres Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1edbi c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng ngay sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Hazard l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\u201d, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft t\u00f4i v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb h\u1ecd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/023624-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Hazard. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0nh cho Hazard v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Real Madrid sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Barcelona. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Andres Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard vo dich FA Cup\" title=\"Eden Hazard vo dich FA Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/chelsea-chi-100-trieu-bang-de-giu-chan-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u01b0a tin Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m Hazard, Coutinho, Messi v\u00e0 Suarez v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n 200 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 Hazard. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 cho Chelsea s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam sao tr\u1ebb Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Hazard. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Barca t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 155 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Dembele t\u1eeb Borussia Dormund. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng b\u1ecf r\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018 cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh ra ch\u1ec9 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nh\u00fan nh\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/he-lo-2-tan-binh-tiep-theo-se-duoc-barca-cong-bo-trong-tuan-toi-187-191356.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi-180-191340.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-croatia-danh-tieng-cho-real-madrid-va-barcelona-421-191189.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-191187.html\">Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4310","checkdouble":"191467"},{"date":"18:28 17/07","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho: Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/jorginho-chia-khoa-thanh-cong-cua-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jorginho l\u00e0 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u00e0 Chelsea k\u00edch n\u1ed5 \u1edf m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Con s\u1ed1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 The Blues b\u1ecf ra cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 khi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 Jorginho.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Maurizio Sarri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge v\u1edbi hy v\u1ecdng mang l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi h\u01a1n cho Chelsea. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-chelsea-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-sarri-172-191180.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng mang t\u00ean Jorginho</span>, Sarri \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00fap The Blues ch\u01a1i b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Napoli m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c trong s\u1ed1 5 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u \u00c2u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Jorginho ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Andrea Pirlo t\u1ea1i Serie A (218) d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri n\u0103m 2015.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mua Jorginho Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/182250-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Giovanni Trapattoni t\u1eebng khen Jorginho s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n thi\u00ean t\u00e0i v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u00f3c c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nh\u1ea1y b\u00e9n. Radja Nainggolan c\u0169ng t\u1eebng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 th\u00e1n ph\u1ee5c khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n n\u1ed5i Jorginho tr\u00ean s\u00e2n: \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1y theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng th\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ec7t l\u1eed\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Italia t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 15. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Hellas Verona. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ea1ng t\u01b0 Sambonifacese n\u0103m 2010, Jorginho m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Claudio Valigi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng Jorginho c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJorginho m\u1edbi 19 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb Sambonifacese, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0o th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Verona. Anh c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n l\u00ean ch\u01a1i \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 hai. Roberto Bordin, tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd HLV xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Jorginho thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Verona c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u k\u00fd \u1ee9c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1ec1 Jorginho. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e0ng trai khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u1edf Hellas Verona. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. L\u00fd do gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed7i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i nh\u1edd t\u00f4i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c kh\u00e2u c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n lu\u00f4n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Napoli, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 nh\u1edd anh qu\u00e1 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u00e0 HLV Sarri x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, Jorginho c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f9i xu\u1ed1ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Jorginho nh\u01b0ng c\u1eed \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Tien-ve-Jorginho-Chia-khoa-thanh-cong-cua-Sarri-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea hay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Napoli, Jorginho kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Benitez. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Joao Santos t\u1eebng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Benitez \u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u00ec c\u00f3 l\u1ebd qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a Jorginho t\u1ea1i Naples s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Benitez th\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u00edt l\u00ean b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p ng\u1eafn. May m\u1eafn cho Jorginho l\u00e0 Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 s\u1eeda l\u1ea1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. V\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111an b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng, Jorginho nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1eaft x\u00edch quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jorginho c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1eady nh\u1edd kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u01b0ng Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191438.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Morata n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4309","checkdouble":"191455"},{"date":"05:39 18/07","title":"Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 Alisson, Liverpool chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/liverpool-muon-mua-alisson-gia-62-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma. Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. The Kop nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin vui t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Roma r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm. Real t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32 trong khi Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/liverpool-muon-mua-alisson-gia-62-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNghe \u0111\u00e2u, Liverpool v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Roma, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c sau khi b\u00e1n Mohamed Salah cho ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRoma \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Liverpool l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Kop r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00fac m\u1eafc gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho hay Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius doi dien tuong lai bat on sau man trinh dien te hai o chung ket Champions League.\" title=\"Loris Karius \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/Dan-anh-du-doan-Karius-tro-lai-manh-me-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Karius</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlphonse Areola c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain r\u1ed3i Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Roma. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Liverpool, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng Loris Karius, Simon Mignolet hay Danny Ward kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho c\u00e1c tham v\u1ecdng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat Like m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u00f3 hai n\u1eefa Roma v\u00e0 Liverpool chia \u0111\u00f4i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y ng\u1ea7m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chi-160-trieu-euro-klopp-muon-mang-ve-liverpool-3-ngoi-sao-187-191414.html\">Chi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro, Klopp mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Liverpool 3 ng\u00f4i sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-bi-quen-lang-172-191409.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-191370.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff-172-191368.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4308","checkdouble":"191465"},{"date":"06:00 18/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ch\u1ec9 ra b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/robert-pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n binh s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Stephan Lichsteiner, Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam 1, 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sokratis l\u00e0 1 trong 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 tin Arsenal t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kingsley Coman c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hai b\u00ean c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh s\u1ed1 1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Song trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 Robert Pires l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Unai Emery, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/robert-pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Emery l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Emery, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEmery \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u1ecb HLV n\u00e0y s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Premier League b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 tu\u1ea7n sau, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-emery-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-172-191065.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wenger-bat-bai-khoi-arsenal-vikante-172-190866.html\">Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4307","checkdouble":"191466"},{"date":"06:42 18/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c CSKA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Evgeniy Giner, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CSKA Moscow x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Golovin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i\u201d n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, \u0111i b\u00f3ng hay tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, Golovin \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra Golovin \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1eeb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 t\u1ea1i CSKA. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/20180614T165656Z_486856268_RC1444D35830_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPRUSSAU.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Arsenal, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin h\u00f4m qua r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>CSKA ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Evgeniy Giner c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nga cho bi\u1ebft b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Golovin s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng phung ph\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Golovin ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng ngay ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft\u201d, Giner n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Sport24 c\u1ee7a Nga. \u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f4ng khai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Monaco (Vadim Vasilyev) gh\u00e9 th\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Golovin. C\u00f2n Chelsea? Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 CLB m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Golovin s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129, ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nga. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191438.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Morata n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard-172-191432.html\">Mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-nguoi-thay-the-hazard-172-191418.html\">Chelsea chi 115 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Hazard</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4306","checkdouble":"191470"}]}